	<h1 class="title">什么是原汁原味且拥有明显中国特色的…迪士尼乐园？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">David Barboza and Brooks Barnes</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-16 14:24:01 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/12189/medium/12189.jpg?1437012664" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="12189" data-title="《什么是原汁原味且拥有明显中国特色的…迪士尼乐园？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/12189/medium/12189.jpg?1437012664" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/12189.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
